From: Surface Pro 11 bring-up <noreply@example.invalid>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] debian.qcom-x1e: update annotations for 7.1.3-jg-0 build

When building the jg/ubuntu-qcom-x1e-7.1.3-jg-0 tag in an Ubuntu 26.04
container, olddefconfig changes several annotation-visible symbols due to
the newer toolchain (GCC 15, rustc 1.93). Update annotations to match the
generated config.

